 will fly this telescope on a\nhigh-altitude balloon later this year.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2016 10:44:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2016 05:24:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2017 03:21:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-08"}
