tant wind speed. If this conclusion is confirmed by\nmore sophisticated wind modelling. it might provide an interesting\nobservational constraint on the properties of stellar winds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2016 12:26:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-01"}
