M set of equations\nsupports the lattice temperature modulation behaviour obtained in the\nsimulations and reveals that in-depth diffusion length is a determining\nparameter in the dispersion relation of unstable modes. Finally it is discussed\nhow the change in optical properties can intensify the modulation-related\neffects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2016 14:08:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-12"}
