 ALMA and LIGO, other\ncountries have bolstered their mm-wave and cm-wave facilities; it is critical\nthat U.S. scientists have ready access to a large filled aperture to remain at\nthe forefront of research.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2016 15:46:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-10"}
